data.description: This home is impeccable. Oversized family room opens to large incredible kitchen (3 ovens!) with separate eating area & formal dining. 3 bedrooms on main floor! High end finishes from the beautiful hardwoods to the double trey ceilings, coffered ceilings & trim detail throughout.  Entertaining space for family & friends indoor & out from theater room, bonus room, outdoor fireplace with built in seating, screened porch & privacy. Fridge, irrigation, nest cameras all included, better than new construction!
data.whatILove: There is so much to love about this home, neighborhood and location. With friendly neighbors that are welcoming to game nights and social gatherings, while at the same time having privacy. The walking trails in neighborhood that lead to the reservoir are an excellent plus. The home itself, it looks so brand new, has a great driveway set up for when there are several driving teenagers or entertaining, and that leads me to the inside. The floor plan is my personal favorite, with a master on one side and two bedrooms on the other all on the main floor, you can live completely downstairs and let guests or teens have an upstairs suite. Upstairs not only is the bonus room with wet bar space fantastic, there is a huge storage closet for seasonal items, a full movie theatre room, 2 bedrooms and a full bath. The backyard is private, boasts a fireplace and screened porch, truly a wonderful place to call home!
